&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;Cyber Solutions Architect&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;We are looking for a highly skilled and motivated Cyber Solutions Architect&amp;nbsp;to join&amp;nbsp;our growing team. &amp;nbsp;As a key member of our sales organization, you will work closely with the sales team to understand customer needs,&amp;nbsp;demonstrate&amp;nbsp;the capabilities of our cybersecurity solutions, and provide technical&amp;nbsp;expertise&amp;nbsp;throughout the sales process. The ideal candidate will have a strong technical background in cybersecurity, excellent communication skills, and the ability to translate complex technical concepts into compelling value propositions for our clients. &amp;nbsp;Candidates&amp;nbsp;who&amp;nbsp;desire&amp;nbsp;a fast-paced environment while advancing their knowledge of all the latest technologies to help our clients prevent, detect, remediate, and&amp;nbsp;recover from&amp;nbsp;threats are highly encouraged to apply.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Redapt Inc. is a pioneering world-class data center infrastructure integrator, technology engineering firm, and cloud services provider. Our teams focus on delivering innovative solutions and services that power our customers&#39; most demanding applications and enable them to extract powerful insights from data that drive true business value.  &amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key&amp;nbsp;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;u&gt;Solution Demonstrations&lt;/u&gt;: Conduct compelling product demonstrations to&amp;nbsp;showcase&amp;nbsp;the features and benefits of our cybersecurity solutions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
