&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;u&gt;Proof of Value (PoVs)&lt;/u&gt;: Design and execute proof of value to&amp;nbsp;validate&amp;nbsp;the effectiveness of partner ISV and cyber technology in customer environments.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;u&gt;Customized Presentations&lt;/u&gt;: Develop and deliver customized presentations and technical proposals that align with customer needs and&amp;nbsp;objectives.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
