&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GenAI Consultant&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Redapt Inc. is a pioneering world-class data center infrastructure integrator, technology engineering firm, and cloud services provider. Our teams focus on delivering innovative solutions and services that power our customers&#39; most demanding applications and enable them to extract powerful insights from data that drive true business value.  &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly skilled GenAI Consultant to help design, build, and deploy enterprise-grade generative AI solutions leveraging AWS services and modern AI engineering practices. This individual will work closely with clients, architects, developers, and business stakeholders to implement scalable AI-driven applications focused on automation, conversational AI, and intelligent workflows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will possess strong expertise in AWS Bedrock, AWS Lambda, and Prompt Engineering, along with experience translating business requirements into practical GenAI solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and implement generative AI solutions using AWS Bedrock&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop serverless AI workflows and integrations utilizing AWS Lambda&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create, optimize, and maintain high-quality prompts for LLM-based applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and enhance AI-powered assistants, chatbots, and automation platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to gather requirements and recommend AI-driven strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrate foundation models and APIs into enterprise applications and workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct prompt testing, tuning, and evaluation to improve model performance and response quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support architecture discussions, solution design, and AI best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with proof-of-concepts (POCs), demos, and customer workshops&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure security, scalability, and operational excellence across AI solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current on emerging GenAI, LLM, and cloud technologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Skills &amp;amp; Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong hands-on experience with AWS Bedrock&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building serverless applications with AWS Lambda&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid understanding of Prompt Engineering methodologies and LLM optimization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience integrating APIs and cloud-native services within AWS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of generative AI concepts, foundation models, and conversational AI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience developing AI-driven applications or intelligent workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with Python, JavaScript, or other scripting languages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of AI governance, responsible AI practices, and model limitations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication and client-facing consulting skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with vector databases and embeddings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exposure to Amazon Lex, Amazon Connect, or conversational AI platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AWS Certifications (Solutions Architect, AI Practitioner, or Developer Associate)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with LangChain, Semantic Kernel, or similar AI orchestration frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consulting or customer-facing delivery experience&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
