&lt;p&gt;As a Sr. Client Director, you will be responsible for driving new business by leveraging your existing client relationships and pursuing net-new opportunities across targeted enterprise accounts. You will&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;bring an established book of business&lt;/strong&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;hunt for new logos&lt;/strong&gt;, and expand Redapt’s presence across greenfield territories. By advocating the power of our end-to-end technology solutions and collaborating with our specialized practice teams, you will guide opportunities through the full sales cycle — from prospecting and discovery to solution design and close.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Using your business acumen and passion for technology, you will help organizations accelerate their digital transformation across infrastructure, applications, data and cybersecurity solutions. This includes identifying and qualifying opportunities around cloud expansion, data center modernization, and emerging technologies. You will also complete training in core datacenter technologies — including server, storage, networking, and software — to ensure deep alignment with Redapt’s technical capabilities.&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
