&lt;p&gt;Redapt Inc. is a pioneering world-class data center infrastructure integrator, technology engineering firm, and cloud services provider. Our teams focus on delivering innovative solutions and services that power our customers&#39; most demanding applications and enable them to extract powerful insights from data that drive true business value. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Virtual Chief Technology Officer (VCTO)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: Vegas, NV&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Redapt Inc. is a pioneering data center infrastructure integrator, technology engineering firm, and cloud services provider. Our teams deliver innovative solutions that power demanding applications and extract powerful insights from data to drive true business value.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Virtual Chief Technology Officer (vCTO) on our team, we’re looking for you to provide world-class executive advisory services as well as support the Redapt sales team in pre-sales calls and meetings, speak at events, attend or lead podcasts/fireside chats. The vCTO engages in thought leadership, new solution development and continuously builds expertise to Redapt’s solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a vCTO focusing on Data and AI, your main duties include supporting sales, services, and implementation teams with leadership, deep architectural skills, and mentoring. You will ensure we deliver innovative, high-quality, scalable technology solutions while collaborating across functions. The ideal candidate has over 10 years of experience as a CTO, CIO, or VP of Technology with expertise in data architecture, analytics, data science,&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;DataOps&lt;/u&gt;, and AI deployments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Senior Data and AI Architect with deep knowledge of data architecture, AI, and the sales process. The candidate should excel in communicating with executive teams and possess extensive expertise in Partner programs and funding opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
